{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "cab89d53-f6d0-4493-ae44-412fc4443c88", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/cab89d53-f6d0-4493-ae44-412fc4443c88@1.pkg/1772602465090/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602465888", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/cab89d53-f6d0-4493-ae44-412fc4443c88@1.pkg/1772602465090/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602465888"}, "identifier": "cab89d53-f6d0-4493-ae44-412fc4443c88", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A 选项“掂记”应为“惦记” ；C 选项“屹立”的“屹”应读“yì” ；D 选项“诬篾”应为“诬蔑”</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/cab89d53-f6d0-4493-ae44-412fc4443c88@1.pkg/item.json?v=1752199733484", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>竹<span class=\"dot\">篾</span>（miè） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;茅<span class=\"dot\">坪</span>（píng） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">掂</span>记 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;千<span class=\"dot\">钧</span>一发</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>坚<span class=\"dot\">韧</span>（rèn） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">掰</span>断（bāi） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">&nbsp;搀</span>扶 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;风<span class=\"dot\">欺</span>雪压</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p><span class=\"dot\">攒</span>起来（zǎn） &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">屹</span>立（qì） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">啃</span>咬 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">昂</span>首挺胸</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>云<span class=\"dot\">霄</span>（xiāo） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">哺</span>育（bǔ） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;诬<span class=\"dot\">篾</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不可名<span class=\"dot\">状</span></p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c